{"id":311416,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-上海民众第112次向市人大请愿要求诉权（图/","date":"2013-08-31T00:05:04Z","modified":"2013-08-31T00:05:04Z","title":"维权网 | 上海民众第112次向市人大请愿要求诉权（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span>日星期一下午<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>时左右，上海<span lang=\"EN-US\">81</span>名维权民众来到上海市人大常委会人民来访接待大厅，等候人大接待员接待。每次接待，代表们都请求人大常委会及人大代表履行法定职责，尊重法律，维护公民诉权，清除司法不作为，彻底铲除司法腐败根源。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span><span>今天大家推荐冯正虎、陈建芳、邱贵荣、黄尧年、崔福芳等<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>人为<span lang=\"EN-US\">112</span>次维护公民诉权的代表，<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>名代表进入<span lang=\"EN-US\">105</span>人大接待室，向人大费老师重申民众要求归还公民诉权的意愿。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>冯正虎询问费老师：<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span>日你向上海当局最高领导韩正汇报，至今已二个月了，韩正书记及上海市委有何回应吗？费老师答道：还没有。冯正虎指出：“公民诉权问题不解决，公民只能一次又一次的到信访部门信访。如果诉讼畅通了，我们也不用每周一到人大来集访了” 。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span><span>唱一曲国际歌被劳教一年的崔福芳本月<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>日从上海女子劳教所获释，今天她也参加维护公民诉权的请愿活动。她与费老师打招呼：“我们一年多不见了” 。费老师笑着点头。崔福芳反映了受冤劳教及有关部门违法拘留的一些情况，要求费老师向人大常委会反映，并希望早日解决公民诉权被侵犯的问题。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span><span>上海市民向市人大常委会已经连续进行了<span lang=\"EN-US\">112</span>次请愿<span lang=\"EN-US\">——</span>“我要立案，捍卫法律，还我诉权”，人大已向上海最高当局<span lang=\"EN-US\">——</span>中共上海市委汇报，上海市委应当与上海市人大共同承担起捍卫法律、维护公民诉权的责任。宪法赋予公民的权利是任何组织或个人不得侵犯和剥夺的，地方法院剥夺公民诉权，为违法犯罪的腐败恶势力保驾护航，已经构成严重渎职。中共上海市委、市人大常委会应该追究渎职的院长、立案庭庭长，整顿法院，保证公民诉讼自由，畅通诉讼通道。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参与第<span lang=\"EN-US\">112</span>次“我要立案——维护公民诉权”行动的市民维权代表有<span lang=\"EN-US\">81</span>人（名单详见附图）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>“我要立案——维护公民诉权”行动请与下述市民代表联系：<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>冯正虎（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13524687100</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>焦东海（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13801802454</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>鲁<span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span>俊（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13651817422</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>赵迪迪（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13482668387</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>朱金娣（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13042111402</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>沈佩兰（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13764885120</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>王扣玛（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13601929155</span>）【为十八大维稳，至今被迫害关押】<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>童国菁（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13917920278</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>崔福芳（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13564097383</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>王蓉华（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13162424968</span>） <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>邱贵荣（<span lang=\"EN-US\">15001903401</span>） <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>刘洪贤（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13524850369</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>郑培培（<span lang=\"EN-US\">02153963826</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>孙建敏（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13671947476</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>陈建芳（<span lang=\"EN-US\">15026516445</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span>日<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-AaZbEp49Yqs/UiCvl2vXW3I/AAAAAAAAnho/BpvnQEKVgaI/s1600/P.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-AaZbEp49Yqs/UiCvl2vXW3I/AAAAAAAAnho/BpvnQEKVgaI/s320/P.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-N8Pd2uXK90A/UiCvgq0Wp6I/AAAAAAAAnhg/YsQ6bOEnN_w/s1600/P1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"213\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-N8Pd2uXK90A/UiCvgq0Wp6I/AAAAAAAAnhg/YsQ6bOEnN_w/s320/P1.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-rcEWOFDKa9I/UiCvrEgZGqI/AAAAAAAAnh4/im3J7adLi94/s1600/img001.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-rcEWOFDKa9I/UiCvrEgZGqI/AAAAAAAAnh4/im3J7adLi94/s1600/img001.jpg\" width=\"232\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-U7B5O1cn9Yc/UiCvmwEq8PI/AAAAAAAAnhw/bIc211ey1ho/s1600/img002.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-U7B5O1cn9Yc/UiCvmwEq8PI/AAAAAAAAnhw/bIc211ey1ho/s1600/img002.jpg\" width=\"232\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Mx3044-zV_c/UiCvx16XheI/AAAAAAAAniA/oJpcyIunFUk/s1600/img003.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Mx3044-zV_c/UiCvx16XheI/AAAAAAAAniA/oJpcyIunFUk/s320/img003.jpg\" width=\"232\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}